3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses decision making to minimize power consumption, which involves control systems. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to make delay-aware decisions. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the use of algorithms to minimize power consumption.
